title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses the business of television rights in college football. Mike Florio joins to discuss Russ Wilson's new contract and how it could affect Lamar Jackson. And University of Cincinnati Head Football Coach Luke Fickell shares his expectations for this Bearcats team this season.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
